Brytavious Lakeith Chambers (amụrụ na Septemba 20, 1996), nke a maara dịka Tay Keith, bụ ónyé America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ na onye na-ede egwu. A maara ya nke ọma màkà iso mepụta egwu Travis Scott nke 2018 "Sicko Mode", na-arị elu na nọmba otu na Billboard Hot 100, BlocBoy JB's "Look Alive", na-eru na nọmba 5 na Hot 100, na Drake's "Nonstop", na-erute na nọmba abụọ
Ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta mbipụta na Warner Chappell Music ma bụrụ ónyé otu BMI.

Keith bụ ónyé kasị nta n'ezinụlọ n'ime ụmụnne ya nwoke abụọ na ụmụnne ya nwanyị abụọ.
